data.description: This is Spanish Walk at its' finest! Come explore this enticing 3BR/2.5BA home situated on an exclusive community street positioned for optimal privacy.  Select upgrades in this stylish home are without rival in Spanish Walk with a transformed, magazine worthy primary bathroom, impressive tile flooring, sizeable paver courtyard, inviting open kitchen with granite counters and a top of the line epoxy garage floor! Desirable first level primary suite floor plan with additional bedrooms and loft located upstairs fulfills both practical and privacy needs for multiple audiences. With 3 community pools and spas, upgraded fitness center and well-maintained grounds with sidewalks throughout for leisurely strolls, this charming, low HOA gated community is located in the center of the Coachella Valley with easy access to I-10 and all major roads through the desert. Spanish Walk is also serviced by Imperial Irrigation District (IID) for a considerable savings opportunity on electric bills. Enjoy the combination of living in a fashionable home with the ease of a low maintenance Spanish Walk lifestyle!
